Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_grxstsrd

Receive Status Debug Read Register, Device Mode (GRXSTSRD)

A read to the Receive Status Debug Read register returns the contents of the top of the Receive FIFO. This Description is only valid when the core is in Device Mode. For Host Mode use USBC_GRXSTSRH instead. NOTE: GRXSTSRH and GRXSTSRD are physically the same register and share the same offset in the O2P USB core. The offset difference shown in this document is for software clarity and is actually ignored by the hardware.
